09:06.916 --> 09:09.951
Ho ho ho ho ho ho ho ho!

09:10.019 --> 09:11.219
You take care, Dylan.

09:11.287 --> 09:15.390
Ho ho ho ho ho ho ho ho ho!

09:15.424 --> 09:17.425
Look, I...

09:17.493 --> 09:19.277
Can you stop laughing
for a second

09:19.312 --> 09:21.874
so I can have a conversation?

09:22.899 --> 09:24.099
Thank you.

09:24.133 --> 09:25.800
Thanks.

09:25.868 --> 09:27.969
Come on.

09:28.004 --> 09:29.871
Hey, guys,
I'm gonna head home early.

09:29.906 --> 09:31.206
I got a case
of No-adoption-itis.

09:31.240 --> 09:33.208
You looking
to adopt a child, Cat?

09:33.242 --> 09:35.377
Yeah. Why?
You know of one?

09:35.411 --> 09:39.249
Well, I think I know
where you can find one.

09:39.381 --> 09:40.886
Where?

09:40.921 --> 09:42.850
Same guy who got me
the Cigarillos.

09:42.885 --> 09:44.386
He lives about a mile
and a half that way.

09:44.453 --> 09:45.761
- Okay.
- Japanese guy.

09:45.812 --> 09:47.032
Oh! Okay, cool.

09:47.123 --> 09:48.938
I thought you were talking about
the orphan kid over there,

09:48.992 --> 09:52.327
who was talking to himself
and I was like, "No way!"

09:52.361 --> 09:54.078
Come on, Dr. Santa Claus.

09:54.897 --> 09:57.984
So, where are we gonna live?

09:59.102 --> 10:00.535
