10:00.569 --> 10:01.490
♪ This is great ♪

10:01.535 --> 10:03.187
♪ Thank you all so much for... ♪

10:03.472 --> 10:04.639
Oh!

10:04.706 --> 10:08.176
Captain Beach-House,
you're so strong!

10:09.145 --> 10:10.378
What was that?

10:10.413 --> 10:14.950
Oh, I'm sorry for neglecting you,
Olde Tyme Strongman.

10:14.984 --> 10:16.418
Oh!

10:16.452 --> 10:21.122
Oh, Drunk Daddy,
your stubble's so rough.

10:21.157 --> 10:24.092
Yeah, just like that.
You know how I like it.

10:24.126 --> 10:27.228
Oh, I love it when you drink.

10:27.296 --> 10:28.964
Oh, yeah, that's right.

